column2: select top #  m.*,ph.ra as RA_SDSS, ph.dec as Dec_SDSS, pz.z as PhotoZ, pz.zerr as PhotoZ_Err,  ph.dered_u, ph.dered_g, ph.dered_r, ph.dered_i, ph.dered_z,  ph.err_u, ph.err_g, ph.err_r, ph.err_i, ph.err_z,  absMagU, absMagG, absMagR, absMagI, absMagZ,  kcorrU, kcorrG, kcorrR, kcorrI, kcorrZ from  PhotoObj as ph, PhotoZ as pz, mydb.GRG_#_Env as m where  ph.objid = pz.objid  and (ph.ra>=m.RA_deg-# and ph.ra<=m.RA_deg+#)  and (ph.dec>=m.Dec_deg-# and ph.dec<=m.Dec_deg+#)  and (pz.z >= m.z-# and pz.z <= m.z+#)   and ph.type = #  and ph.clean = #  and ph.u > # and ph.g > # and ph.r > # and ph.i > # and ph.z > #
